    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317330/extras/45f68c587fa821a733c142fb335ec451.poster.avif?t=1750747909\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317330/extras/45f68c587fa821a733c142fb335ec451.webm?t=1750747909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317330/extras/45f68c587fa821a733c142fb335ec451.mp4?t=1750747909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你是谁？</h2>一个自杀了的女人。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你在哪里？</h2>3 间超现实的六面房间里。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >房间里有什么？</h2>要破译的秘密信息、要翻译的摩尔斯电码、要记录的隐藏线索、要计算的复杂方程、以及更多具有挑战性的谜题；大约 <strong>2-3 小时 </strong>的独特解谜体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你为什么在这里？</h2>为了揭晓一场悲惨的事故，和我的死因。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >还有什么？</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>弹钢琴</li><li>喂鹦鹉</li><li>拍照片</li><li>种种子</li><li>能听的耳朵</li><li>要给的心脏</li><li>在地上的板凳</li><li>和更多</li><li>(没有猫)</li></ul>",
